==鐵路==
北馬其頓國內鐵路總長度{{convert|925|km|mi|abbr=on}}<ref>[http://mz.com.mk/Uploads/Objava_na_mreza_za_2009.pdf  Objava na Mreza] {{Wayback|url=http://mz.com.mk/Uploads/Objava_na_mreza_za_2009.pdf |date=20111009100450 }}. [[Macedonian_Railways|Macedonian Railways]]</ref>，由[[馬其頓鐵路|馬其頓鐵路]]負責運營。目前北馬其頓有修建新的鐵路線的計劃<ref>{{cite journal | journal=[[Railway_Gazette_International|Railway Gazette International]] | date=April 2006 | url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view//world-bank-funds-mz-split.html | title=World Bank funds MZ split | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527223635/http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/world-bank-funds-mz-split.html | archivedate=2012-05-27 | access-date=2016-02-22 }}</ref>。北馬其頓也有開往塞爾維亞、科索沃和希臘等鄰國的國際列車。

